http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2015/04/150417085300.htm?utm_source=feedburner&utm_medium=feed&utm_campaign=Feed%3A+sciencedaily+%28Latest+Science+News+--+ScienceDaily%29
[To avoid another large outbreak, greater flexibility must be provided to medical trials for diseases like Ebola virus disease. Even if the current epidemic is eventually contained, the world will still be largely unprepared for the next epidemic]

