17 Apr 2015 World Bank: increases aid to Ebola-hit West Africa
http://allafrica.com/stories/201504171854.html?viewall=1
[The World Bank announced on Fri 17 Apr 2015, it will provide USD 650 million over the next 18 months, bringing its total assistance so far to USD 1.62 billion]

